OL,3,CFarmers eligible to receive up to
OL,4,C#25,000 of support in wake of flooding
OL,6,FThe government had originally
OL,7,Fannounced in January its intention to
OL,8,Fopen the fund, following severe
OL,9,Fflooding caused by Storm Henk.
OL,11,FFarmers across the UK have previously
OL,12,Ftold ITV News they have been dating
OL,13,Fback to last October.
OL,15,FThe wet weather comes at a time where
OL,16,F, with March recorded to be the tenth
OL,17,Fmonth in a row to be the hottest on
OL,18,Frecord for the time of year. Last
OL,19,Fmonth also saw England experience 62%
OL,20,Fmore rainfall than an average March.
