OL,6,FHow does the scheme work?
OL,8,FUnder the scheme, eligible farmers
OL,9,Fcould receive grants ranging between
OL,10,F#500 to #25,000 in order to return
OL,11,Ftheir land to the condition it was in
OL,12,Fbefore flooding occurred.
OL,14,FCurrently, the FRF is only open to
OL,15,Ffarms in counties deemed eligible by
OL,16,FDefra, including:
OL,18,FThis is because the government's - a
OL,19,Fscheme which the FRF helps to form -
OL,20,Fis currently active in all of these
OL,21,Fcounties.
