OL,6,FFarming Minister Mark Spencer said: "I
OL,7,Fknow how difficult this winter has
OL,8,Fbeen for farmers, with extreme weather
OL,9,Fsuch as Storm Henk having a
OL,10,Fdevastating impact on both cropping
OL,11,Fand grazing, as well as damaging
OL,12,Fproperty and equipment.
OL,14,F"The Farming Recovery Fund will
OL,15,Fsupport farmers who suffered
OL,16,Funinsurable damage with grants of up
OL,17,Fto #25,000, and sits alongside broader
OL,18,Fsupport in our farming schemes to
OL,19,Fimprove flood resilience."
